{
  "texts": [
    "While current LLM-based AI systems excel at synthesis and implementation, they have yet to consistently demonstrate genuine creativity.",
    "The spark of insight that identifies a truly novel research question, the intuition that connects disparate phenomena, the judgment that recognizes profound implicationsthese remain at present human contributions.",
    "AI agents are superb research assistants but not yet independent researchers.The gap, however, may be narrowing faster than we anticipate.",
    "The capability spiral documented in this paper-where AI helps build better AI, which enables still more sophisticated systems-suggests an accelerating pace of development.",
    "If human-level AI emerges across all cognitive domains, as many AI pioneers predict, the automation of economic research becomes not a question of if but when."
  ]
}